---
title: Loaded Greek Potato Wedges with Lemon-Yogurt Sauce and Feta
description: Loaded Greek fries are a restaurant favourite you can easily make in your own kitchen. Filled with pork, feta and yogurt sauce, these crisp wedges are sure to become a hit with your family.

